com.teamwork.autocomplete.adapter

Interface OnTokensChangedListener<Model>


  • public interface OnTokensChangedListener<Model>
    Listener interface for components tied to an TypeAdapterDelegate that need a callback when a full token gets added or removed within the text contents of an editable TextView.

    The detected text token will be matched to an item of type 'Model' by the type adapter and returned in the callback.

    i.e. if the user types '@johndoe' and the handle matches one of the data items in the adapter, the onTokenAdded(CharSequence, Object) method from a subscribed listener will be called with that handle and the associated 'person' model.

    See Also:
    AutoCompleteTypeAdapter.setOnTokensChangedListener(OnTokensChangedListener)
